íŸ@e5c8ead9312a020a71f45024029e5f4b4aa10b3071356efbb42ad96470773587⁄ Title: title: ulimit
Path: Examples
Content:
Print all current limits.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit -a


```
Print specified limits.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit --core-size --data-size --file-size


```
Set limit.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit --core-size 102400


```
Set stack size soft limit.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit -s -S 10240


```
Set virtual memory size hard limit.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit -v -H 10240


```
Set core size limit to unlimited.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ulimit -c unlimited


```
